{"tid":1985533,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"高院下周三就梁天琦暴動罪刑期上訴頒判決","createTime":"2020-04-23T08:00:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-25T20:16:51.000Z","uid":21470,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a946b1b8560f1fda612d5e7c14896a6967458785","tid":1985533,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T08:00:45.000Z","msg":"高院下周三就梁天琦暴動罪刑期上訴頒判決<br />\n23.04.2020 15:56<br />\n<br />\n高等法院上訴庭將會在下星期三，就2016年旺角騷亂案中，本土民主前線前發言人梁天琦的暴動罪刑期上訴頒判決，同案另外兩名被告盧建民及黃家駒的上訴亦會有判決。<br />\n<br />\n梁天琦前年因為暴動及襲警罪被判囚6年，案中另外兩名被告盧建民和黃家駒，分別判監7年和3年半，3人在去年提出上訴。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1282826&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1282826%26csid%3D261_341&d=7FLALsszV4LuAMmN05fc6hyAur%2Bbp9MVyOkMM5%2FMxDY%3D&h=b622cf51\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1282826&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"07fa4a056a84b716314a0806a93c0088fdedca12","tid":1985533,"uid":76745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T08:02:36.000Z","msg":"終於瞓醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecbb39e2180f139b8c27c0f532e1a819308ff065","tid":1985533,"uid":339805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T08:03:31.000Z","msg":"分分鐘加刑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92e5a1f3bdbee74f6f05d2069f897c8a4f834f3d","tid":1985533,"uid":118647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T08:04:49.000Z","msg":"痴撚線拖咁耐"},{"pid":"54725c51a56d1574a4415fc74f35b23ccae7633d","tid":1985533,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T20:16:51.000Z","msg":"其實預鳩左上訴失敗<br />\n<br />\n你睇而家紅藍官當道就知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n明明大家都認同法治已死<br />\n<br />\n點解仲奢望今次可以撥亂反正<img src=\"/assets